#. BATTLE_FEATURE.PC_ALAN_LIGHTWEIGHT.DESC
msgctxt "BATTLE_FEATURE.PC_ALAN_LIGHTWEIGHT.DESC"
msgid ""
msgstr "在该牌使用前如果所有手牌花费总和<#HILITE>少于等于</>一定数则会获得额外效果。"

